@Terra_Gregorean
$ #Gregorean calendar#
  A Gregorean calendar is a time notation on planet Earth.

 ~Configurations~@Contents@

@Terra_Millenium
$ #Milleniums` calendar#
  A Milleniums` calendar is a years notation by milleniums.

 One "year"    = 1000 years — one millenium.
 One "month"   =  100 years — one century.
 One "week"    =   10 years — one decade.
 One "day"     =    1 year.
 One "hour"    =    1 month.
 One "minute"  =    1 day (approximately!).
 One "second"  =    1 hour.
 One "msec"    =    ⅟₁₀₀₀ (one thousandth) of an hour.

 ~Configurations~@Contents@

