@Terra_Seasons
$ #Earth seasons in calendar#
  In temperate and sub-polar regions, four seasons
based on the Gregorian calendar are generally recognized.
In 1780 the Societas Meteorologica Palatina defined seasons
as groupings of three whole months as identified by the Gregorian calendar.

